sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Search Service
    participant R as Redis
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant ES as Elasticsearch

    C->>S: GET /search?q=... (+ JWT)
    S->>R: lookup per-user cached result
    alt cache hit
        R-->>S: cached hits
        S-->>C: results (cached=true, ~0 ms)
    else cache miss
        S->>PG: resolve visible document ids (ACL)
        S->>ES: query, filtered by visible ids (BM25)
        ES-->>S: ranked hits + highlights
        S->>R: store result with TTL
        S-->>C: results (cached=false)
    end
